  <brief_title>Hemodynamic and Pharmacokinetic Analysis of Oxymetazoline Absorption</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Hemodynamic and Pharmacokinetic Analysis of Oxymetazoline Absorption During Functional Endoscopic or Turbinate Reduction Surgery and From the Nasal Mucosa During Operative Dentistry</official_title>
